      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i have reached out to people and i have talked to professionals. they just give me the same scripts and the same coping mechanisms. it feels like they are just trying to keep me alive for the sake of being alive, not actually helping the pain. they don't get that some things can't be \"fixed\" with breathing exercises or meds. is there really no other way to just... reach a state of peace?",
